<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is based on section 205 of title II of S. 2416, Ninety-eighth Congress, as introduced <date date="1984-03-13">Mar. 13, 1984</date>, and enacted into law by <ref href="/us/pl/98/473">Pub. L. 98–473</ref>.</p>
</note>
